---
const diagram = String.raw`
            ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
            │           atlas-web  (React UI)         │
            │   chat · skills · approvals · forge     │
            │       dashboards · teams · settings     │
            └────────────────────┬────────────────────┘
                                 │  http + sse
                                 ▼
   ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │           atlas-runtime  (Go daemon · port 1984)          │
   │                                                           │
   │   chat svc ── agent loop ── provider dispatch             │
   │       │           │              │                        │
   │       │           │              ├── openai               │
   │       │           │              ├── anthropic            │
   │       │           │              ├── gemini               │
   │       │           │              └── lm studio            │
   │       │           ▼                                       │
   │       │      skills registry  (read · write · execute)    │
   │       │           │                                       │
   │       ▼           ▼                                       │
   │   sqlite     keychain      mind.md / diary.md             │
   └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                                 │
                                 ▼
                ┌──────────────────────────────┐
                │  telegram   discord   ...    │
                └──────────────────────────────┘
`;
---
<section id="architecture" class="border-b border-border">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mb-16 flex items-baseline gap-4" data-reveal>
      <span class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">// 02</span>
      <h2 class="font-mono text-2xl text-text md:text-3xl"><span data-typed-heading>how it works</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] lg:items-center">
      <div class="arch-frame relative overflow-x-auto rounded border border-border bg-surface p-6 shadow-glow-soft" data-reveal>
        <span class="pointer-events-none absolute -inset-px rounded border border-accent/0 transition-[border-color] duration-700"></span>
        <span class="arch-scan pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-12 opacity-30" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <pre class="font-mono text-[11px] leading-snug text-text-2 md:text-xs"><code>{diagram}</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-md space-y-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-2" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 180ms;">
        <p>
          The runtime is a single Go binary installed as a launchd LaunchAgent. It serves the
          web UI, brokers AI provider calls, and dispatches skills.
        </p>
        <p>
          Everything that matters — conversations, memories, agent definitions, skill state — lives
          in <span class="text-text font-mono">~/Library/Application Support/ProjectAtlas/</span>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Secrets sit in the macOS Keychain. No <code class="font-mono text-text">.env</code> files.
          No telemetry. The daemon stops when you tell it to.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .arch-scan {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,255,153,0.18), transparent);
    animation: arch-scan 4.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes arch-scan {
    0%   { transform: translateY(0);  opacity: 0; }
    20%  { opacity: 0.6; }
    100% { transform: translateY(360px); opacity: 0; }
  }
  .arch-frame:hover > span:first-of-type { border-color: rgba(0,255,153,0.35); }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .arch-scan { display: none; }
  }
</style>
